=\sqrt{\frac{c^2-v_x^2}{c^2-c_x^2}}=\sqrt{\frac{c_x^2}{v_x^2}}=\frac{\beta_c}{\beta_v}=\frac{\alpha_x}{\delta_x}&&\\
